<h2 class="h2 copy__heading"></h2>
<h3 class="sub-heading copy__sub-heading">Episode 1: Embracing technology and collaboration for real-time liquidity (15 mins)</h3>
<div class="copy__body"><p><strong>Hosted by Amanda Boston, Receivables GTM Lead and Tom Leitch, Director of Sales and Business Development at Bottomline TreasuryXpress.</strong></p>
<p>This introductory episode focuses on what digitisation is needed in your organisation, how that impacts teams and what you can do to foster collaboration.</p></div>
